Mr President, I would like to ask the Commission to adopt a position on the request made in the legislative resolution for the appropriate measure to be taken in order for there to be a modification of the Community Customs Code, a mentioned by Mr Beysen and a I have also expressed.
Mr President, may I start by extending a warm thanks to the Committee on Legal Affairs and the Internal Market for the work it ha carried out on the basis of Mrs Palacio' s report This report encompasses all the question which formed the subject of debate at first reading in March of last year.
I welcome the major overture which have been made with regard to this dossier, which ha been the subject of long and intense discussion within the Council.
