If, a we hope, the party manage to conclude an agreement, the European Union will add it political and financial support to the effort being made by others on the basis of a fair distribution of the burden and will meet the parties' demand to a reasonable extent.
We are prepared to work on securing stability in the region and, in the long term, on safeguarding the permanent welfare of the region through sustainable economic growth and an improved standard of living, so that the people in the region can reap the benefit of peace.
