Mrs Van Lancker' s report is an ambitious one. The rapporteur effectively asks the Commission to intensify the agenda, chiefly in the following areas: Employment, with the framing of a European pact for employment and social cohesion, a concern lifelong training and the introduction of prior cross-border testing of social and fiscal legislation.
