Mr President, Commissioner, lady and gentlemen, first of all I would like to say a warm thank you for the report we have heard about today, and which do not just record what happened in the past, but also pick out the central theme of the present debate, and even incorporate the Commission' s plans.
Competition is not, a ha already been said, an end in itself.
